        TIPS FOR REDUCING <span>PLASTIC WASTE</span>
    </h1>
    <p>
        Reducing plastic waste is essential to protecting our oceans and wildlife. Here are some effective tips to reduce plastic consumption:
    </p>
    <dl>
        <dt>Use reusable bags and bottles: </dt>
        <dd>Invest in reusable shopping bags, bottles, and containers.</dd>
        <dt>Avoid single-use plastics: </dt>
        <dd>Choose products with minimal plastic packaging.</dd>
        <dt>Buy in bulk: </dt>
        <dd>Purchase products in bulk to minimize packaging waste.</dd>
        <dt>Choose natural materials: </dt>
        <dd>Opt for biodegradable or compostable products instead of plastic.</dd>
    </dl>
